{"tid":1628562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港局勢直接影響台灣 柯P斷言：大選差不多結束","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T05:18:36.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17d5ee833ac56ad3d500488fc0d4603d878e702f","tid":1628562,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:34:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20191005/720pix/1570276262_dd4f.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20191005%2F720pix%2F1570276262_dd4f.jpg&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfECrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=cf72fea9\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20191005/720pix/1570276262_dd4f.jpg</a><br />\n港府昨日 (4日)下午宣佈制訂《禁止蒙面規例》，規例今日（5日）凌晨即生效。台北市長柯文哲5今日受訪時談及香港時，特別拿出貓紙，避免重演失言風波，而談到香港紛亂對於台灣的影響時，他表示，香港問題短期內不會解決，「所以總統大選除非有很大轉折，大概也差不多結束」。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲表示，「從6月到現在已經3個多月，短期不會解決」，所以總統大選除非有很大轉折，大概也差不多結束；媒體追問他是否認為蔡英文會連任成功？柯未正面回答，反而意有所指地說，「1對1的話，現在賭盤有賭韓國瑜贏的嗎？應該沒有吧」。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲日前評論香港議題時引用「擦槍走火」，掀起軒然大波，香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒更嚴詞批評要求道歉。似乎為了避免重演失言風波，柯文哲今日被問到香港議題時，特別拿出「貓紙」照稿讀，還強調這是前一天已寫好。<br />\n<br />\n「香港的局面失控，情況令人擔憂」，柯文哲認為，《禁止蒙面規例》顯然是治標不治本，不會有效，只會激化香港政府跟示威者的衝突，「這樣實施下去還是會局面更難收拾」。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲重申，香港當局跟北京政府還是要誠實面對問題，對症下藥，才能平息風暴，「所以重點不是老百姓蒙面不蒙面，而是政府不要把自己的眼睛蒙住」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191005/60119777?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191005%2F60119777%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfECrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=02973d15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191005%2F60119777%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=1589ebe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191005/60119777?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"46700bc69e86b89c191a333cfd288b942f3cd049","tid":1628562,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfECrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=d9a7e291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a>"},{"pid":"fd0ff3b01d2d20fbb69de51afe6ee3856b4d2363","tid":1628562,"uid":296410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>...「所以重點不是老百姓蒙面不蒙面，而是政府不要把自己的眼睛蒙住」</strong></span></blockquote>"}]}